Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.08,0:00:06.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't regret anything at all! I can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.84,0:00:07.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Because...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.21,0:00:13.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...what I did was definitely not wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.78,0:00:37.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's strange.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.41,0:00:40.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even after...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.29,0:00:44.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}so much time has passed,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.09,0:00:50.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}something can save you,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.84,0:00:54.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}coming in like a storm\Nfrom a completely different direction.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.47,0:01:01.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hina...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.11,0:01:10.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.65,0:01:13.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You are...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.99,0:01:15.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,my lifesaver.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.49,0:01:17.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.24,0:01:20.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll stay with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.29,0:01:24.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rei...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.58,0:01:31.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Even if it takes the rest of my life,\NI will pay you back.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.47,0:03:07.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Small World
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.44,0:03:13.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sniff-sniff.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.11,0:03:18.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sniff-sniff.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.86,0:03:21.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Here's dessert!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.87,0:03:26.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's the cherries that Kiriyama brought over.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.12,0:03:33.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Cherries!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.59,0:03:39.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Kiriyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.97,0:03:51.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}NOM NOM
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.98,0:03:51.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.90,0:03:55.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They smell sour-meow.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.86,0:03:57.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm not crazy about fruit.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.12,0:04:10.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Huh? Are you sleepy, Momo?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.37,0:04:14.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Maybe we should take a bath.\NAlthough it's a bit early...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.67,0:04:23.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So, Hina, do you want to try playing? Shogi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.77,0:04:32.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}SHAKE\NSHAKE\NSHAKE
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.10,0:04:32.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,W-Will you go easy on me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.14,0:04:35.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}SHAKE\NSHAKE\NSHAKE
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.98,0:04:35.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, yes, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.48,0:04:39.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then would you take it upstairs?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.69,0:04:41.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna play some more...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.99,0:04:44.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to give Momo her bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.78,0:04:47.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a9}*Kawamoto House's\Nbath changing room\Nis the living room.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.62,0:04:47.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna play with Rei.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.58,0:04:54.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kiriyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.63,0:04:57.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure that's all you need?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.79,0:05:01.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,HINA
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.79,0:05:01.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}KIRIYAMA
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.21,0:04:59.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.09,0:05:01.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you positive? Just this much?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.55,0:05:02.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.59,0:05:03.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.51,0:05:07.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Apparently the first time in Hina's room...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.80,0:05:05.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then I might be able to win!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.72,0:05:07.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Then let's get started.\N- Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.85,0:05:12.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why aren't I going first?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.93,0:05:14.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you were going easy on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.69,0:05:19.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There's a rule that with handicap shogi,\Nthe player who's short of pieces goes first.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.53,0:05:26.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What? Oh, but... okay. Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.12,0:05:29.03,DefaultLow2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,FIVE MINUTES LATER
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.74,0:05:32.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I-I lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.91,0:05:33.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}GLOOM
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.66,0:05:36.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,One more! One more time!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.71,0:05:43.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Hey, yo, pineapple, lalala,\Na strange magical fruit...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.71,0:05:40.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I know! I'll just play with two pieces,\Nthe king and a gold general!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.55,0:05:46.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Damn it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.64,0:05:49.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why am I so bad at this?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.06,0:05:55.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh. You're taking my Pawn at 5-5?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.52,0:05:56.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Good one.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.94,0:06:01.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If anything, the chairman is skilled at making\Nhis opponents look good and enjoy themselves.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.86,0:06:04.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, here's a hint.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.94,0:06:06.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,With strong pieces, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.15,0:06:07.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,B-Back off and then strike!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.28,0:06:09.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.28,0:06:13.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mr. Yokomizo takes the time to amuse\Nand teach even oddball players. It's great.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.50,0:06:16.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's about communication, Kiriyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.67,0:06:20.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Imagine what your opponent is thinking\Nand what they want to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.84,0:06:22.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then get close to their feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.25,0:06:29.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}In the waiting room\Nof his first shogi event
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.63,0:06:25.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Look at your opponent closely.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.51,0:06:28.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, calm down, and let's take it easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.35,0:06:35.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Look at your opponent closely.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.52,0:06:38.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Okay.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.36,0:06:44.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}STARE
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.28,0:06:48.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Rei.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.11,0:06:50.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I think I'm starting to get the hang of it,\Nso I should be okay for the next one.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.99,0:06:55.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm no match for her!\NThis middle school student is consoling me again!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.04,0:06:59.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, one more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.21,0:07:03.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What's the point of coming here to console her\Nif she's the one consoling you, Rei Kiriyama?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.46,0:07:10.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}And suddenly I felt a lump in my throat.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.84,0:07:14.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}Over the years, how often has this girl smiled{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.81,0:07:17.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}and been considerate\Nof other people's feelings like this?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.77,0:07:24.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hina.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.28,0:07:27.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Listen...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.82,0:07:33.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Will you tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.66,0:07:38.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A little bit at a time is fine.\NAbout what's happening at school...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.34,0:07:50.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, I guess this is what it's like.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.88,0:07:53.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Like everyone is looking from afar.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.22,0:07:59.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hina thought and thought,\Nslowly sharing bits and pieces with me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.35,0:08:03.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Our groups are set up by order of name,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.19,0:08:08.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but at lunch, I can tell\Nthat everyone gets so stiff.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.40,0:08:11.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They hardly ever look at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.70,0:08:16.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's like only my group is at a wake.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.50,0:08:25.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And then the silence is suddenly broken by\Nthe loud laughter of the girls who bullied Chiho.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.50,0:08:30.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Their loud, loud voices...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.88,0:08:32.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Their laughter...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.68,0:08:39.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's like there's an invisible hierarchy\Nwithin our class.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.27,0:08:47.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And your ranking decides\Nhow loud you can laugh
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.61,0:08:53.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,or how much freedom\Nyou're allowed in the classroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.62,0:08:58.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's the atmosphere of Hina's class.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.54,0:09:07.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm sure this is a story that everyone\Nhas experienced at one time or another.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.17,0:09:14.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There shouldn't even be such a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.97,0:09:18.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But... But there is.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.97,0:09:22.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's been there all the time.\NEver since elementary school...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.98,0:09:31.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kiriyama, what is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.32,0:09:33.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That atmosphere...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.90,0:09:38.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Who's cool? Who's not cool?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.74,0:09:42.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When and how is that decided?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.41,0:09:44.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Who decides it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.00,0:09:50.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even though we're all just\Nthe same middle school students.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.13,0:09:56.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Even though we're all just\Nthe same human beings.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.02,0:10:13.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}SILENCE
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.82,0:10:13.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}DISTANCE
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.32,0:10:17.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is that what she really said?\NWhat a loser!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.32,0:10:17.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}CACKLE CACKLE HAHAHA
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.57,0:10:19.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}CACKLE CACKLE CACKLE
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.86,0:10:18.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,CHEW CHEW
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.57,0:10:21.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a1}CHEW CHEW\NMUNCH MUNCH
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.82,0:10:21.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}I'm-telling-you
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.83,0:10:23.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Isn't that nuts?\N- Totally!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.04,0:10:25.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for the meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.71,0:10:31.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's hilarious!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.38,0:10:33.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}GLOOMY
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.92,0:10:33.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Th-This feels so awkward.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.55,0:10:36.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is Kawamoto here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.76,0:10:38.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,T-Takahashi?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.68,0:10:47.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4}STING STING STING
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.23,0:10:47.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Ow! Ow! Ow! Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.85,0:10:50.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}No way. I totally tossed that lightly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.28,0:10:58.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I heard from Kiriyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.74,0:11:04.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,At lunch time...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.99,0:11:06.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}if things get difficult, let's just play catch.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.33,0:11:10.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you want more people,\NI could call my baseball team buddies to join in.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.88,0:11:12.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They're already staring.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.42,0:11:13.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.50,0:11:15.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you, Takahashi!\NThis is outrageous!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.80,0:11:24.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kiriyama came over to my house yesterday\Nto coach us while playing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.52,0:11:29.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see. Now I've got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.19,0:11:31.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,For the Silver at 4-3, you go with Pawn at 3-4.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.40,0:11:35.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Professional shogi players are so amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.48,0:11:37.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's why you're a professional.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.65,0:11:40.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Yeah. I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.45,0:11:42.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Well, it's a surprise tactic.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.49,0:11:45.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Dad and Grandpa were delighted.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.74,0:11:49.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Grandpa's been staying in bed recently,\Nbut he was up and about for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.25,0:11:56.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Invite me over again for curry.\NWith the fried chicken.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.30,0:12:00.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Last time Dad and Grandpa were hogging\NKiriyama, so I couldn't really to talk to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.55,0:12:03.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.01,0:12:07.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.85,0:12:11.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}That can't hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.85,0:12:11.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Small World
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.98,0:12:15.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Letter
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.11,0:12:21.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.00,0:12:31.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.21,0:12:33.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Good game, Kiriyama 5th-Dan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.42,0:12:34.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.06,0:12:53.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,CLENCH
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.65,0:12:54.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}That's four wins!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.98,0:12:55.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.81,0:12:58.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Just one more win and I'll be\Nin the Kishousen preliminary semifinals!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.90,0:13:01.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Things are looking up this month!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.83,0:13:10.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,At the moment, I've got two consecutive wins\Nfor rank-deciding matches.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.04,0:13:15.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm still in the running for Kishousen,\Nthe Lion King Tournament,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.25,0:13:17.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and the Newcomer Tournament.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.51,0:13:22.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to win the Lion King Tournament.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.67,0:13:26.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If I can win in group five\Nand participate in the challenger tournament...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.56,0:13:31.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...then I'll hit my financial target!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.23,0:13:35.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But with the Newcomer Tournament,\Nprize money aside,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.23,0:13:39.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I want to win one more match,\Nget to the finals, and build up momentum.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.78,0:13:52.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right, I need to practice.\NI'm not going to lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.87,0:13:58.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I will become the Newcomer King!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.80,0:14:05.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.05,0:14:06.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.10,0:14:16.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,STOP FLIRTING AROUND, MORON
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.13,0:14:45.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}I couldn't finish eating everything.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.97,0:14:49.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}Is this what they call a stomach ache?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.77,0:14:58.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you show up?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.77,0:15:00.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,T-Takahashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.69,0:15:03.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Bitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.95,0:15:14.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Um, thanks, Takahashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.08,0:15:17.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But today, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.83,0:15:21.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, I think we were\Nin the same class first year.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.71,0:15:24.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Takagi. That's you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.26,0:15:35.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You want to play catch too?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.98,0:15:40.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Here I go! You ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.90,0:15:44.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You go first, Megu!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.36,0:15:46.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No way! I'm scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.11,0:15:48.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be fine! Go on!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.32,0:15:49.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Here I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.41,0:15:53.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,One-two...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.42,0:16:02.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Jerk! You suck!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.00,0:16:04.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm out of here! That guy's insane!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.29,0:16:06.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Megu, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.55,0:16:09.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What, you're leaving already?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.76,0:16:11.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.47,0:16:14.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Takahashi...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.10,0:16:15.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yikes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.72,0:16:18.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Takahashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.02,0:16:22.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They tossed my glove on the ground\Nand ran off.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.77,0:16:28.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The one who changed schools\Nwas Chiho Sakura, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.03,0:16:33.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}During the overnight field trip in second year,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.41,0:16:38.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}the wind blew my bento box over\Nand sand got all over my food.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.87,0:16:44.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then she gave me half of her bento.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.29,0:16:48.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She smiled and said, "Here."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.01,0:16:52.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,At the time, I thought that anyone who\Nshared their own food was a good person.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.59,0:16:58.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So let's play catch anytime.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.97,0:17:05.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I kind of feel like it's a good idea\Nto show them that there are allies too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.99,0:17:15.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.82,0:17:18.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But... I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.08,0:17:21.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Takahashi is so handsome, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.54,0:17:24.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I get it. Now they're envious.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.25,0:17:27.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so sorry.\NI didn't think that far ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.71,0:17:29.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There are bad people-meow.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.63,0:17:31.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No good-meow.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.13,0:17:32.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yeah. Bad-meow.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.80,0:17:36.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, Kiriyama! Don't take it like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.76,0:17:38.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to keep playing catch.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.39,0:17:40.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,After all, it's fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.35,0:17:45.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And Takahashi seems to remember Chiho.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.90,0:17:49.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So I can talk about her,\Nand that makes me really happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.20,0:17:59.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody talks about Chiho in class anymore,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.78,0:18:03.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,so it's like she was never there\Nfrom the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.66,0:18:06.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,One person has gone away.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.17,0:18:09.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So why?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.13,0:18:15.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.97,0:18:17.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Here. Take this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.97,0:18:26.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rei, thank you for always listening to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.02,0:18:33.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're always asking me what I want to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.90,0:18:36.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MIDDLE SCHOOL
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.20,0:18:39.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But I...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.83,0:18:49.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what I want to do...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.38,0:18:52.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...so it's frustrating!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.76,0:19:02.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What do I want to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.97,0:19:07.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I want to yell "Idiots!" and punch them!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.19,0:19:11.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I want to beat the crap out of them!\NI want to do to them what they did to Chiho!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.48,0:19:21.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And then I want them to realize what they did!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.32,0:19:18.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}3-2 SAKURA
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.04,0:19:28.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But it's too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.79,0:19:31.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Chiho's already gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.01,0:19:37.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She sent Chiho a letter,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.05,0:19:40.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but never got a response.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.97,0:19:42.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Instead, she received a response{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.85,0:19:47.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Chiho hasn't got back to school, even here.\NRight now she's in rehab with a counselor\Nat a place called "Heart Care Center."\NChiho would like to write to you, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.60,0:19:46.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}from Chiho's mother.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.10,0:19:48.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, it's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.60,0:19:50.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I make them apologize...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.36,0:19:58.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think Chiho would ever\Nwant to see their faces!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.00,0:20:20.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5}HINATA KAWAMOTO LOVES GUYS\NPERVERTED GIRL\NBITCH IDIOT
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.72,0:20:25.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There's one thing that I realized.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.99,0:20:40.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I had thought...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.86,0:20:46.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...that if things got tough,\Nyou can just get up and leave.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.37,0:20:48.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3-2 KAWAMOTO
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.25,0:20:55.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}When someone treats you improperly...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.00,0:20:59.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}...you don't have to respond in a proper way.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.84,0:21:05.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.98,0:21:14.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Stand up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.27,0:21:16.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Bow!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.02,0:21:19.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}HINATA KAWAMOTO LOVES GUYS\NPERVERTED GIRL\NBITCH IDIOT
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.11,0:21:22.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wh—
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.82,0:21:25.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,M-Ms. Kawamoto, what's the meaning of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.21,0:21:33.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.12,0:21:36.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not the one who wrote it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.63,0:21:47.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Chiho Sakura: Absent/Absent/Absent
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.30,0:21:47.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I think you're misreading it, Ms. Kawamoto.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.35,0:21:52.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You shouldn't turn\Nevery situation into a bad one.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.81,0:21:58.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It was already written on the board\Nwhen I came in this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.70,0:22:15.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A-Anyway, let's begin the lesson.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.46,0:22:18.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ms. Kawamoto, please see me\Nin the faculty room after class.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.30,0:22:28.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, concentrate! Stop your whispering!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.39,0:22:31.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's have a good game.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.93,0:22:36.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}That's right.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.52,0:22:40.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}She's not only in pain.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.03,0:22:43.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}She's angry.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.78,0:22:49.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}In fact, she's seething\Nfrom the pit of her stomach.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.04,0:23:00.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Letter
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.01,0:24:32.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Next Episode Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.01,0:24:37.97,EpNum,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 29
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.39,0:24:34.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, don't look at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.05,0:24:36.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sis, get me a bath towel!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.01,0:24:39.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do?\NIt's terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.10,0:24:42.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Finally! We finally made it to this point!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.15,0:24:45.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the only one who can go\Nfrom our family.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.90,0:24:50.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I bought peaches. Maybe I should've bought\Nice cream instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.03,0:24:58.50,EpNum,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ILLUSTRATION:\NKOZUE AMANO
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.99,0:24:54.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yoohoo, yoohoo, cherries!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.57,0:24:57.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Derere, yummy magical fruit!
